00:23:24.488 --> 00:23:26.490
<i>Deku, you're lonely, huh?</i>

00:23:26.657 --> 00:23:28.367
<i>Did I get labeled a loner</i>
<i>without knowing it?</i>

00:23:28.534 --> 00:23:30.410
